PANAMA
AT
THE FIFA WORLD CUP
Panama has qualified once for the finals of a FIFA World Cup , the 2018 edition .
They directly qualified after securing the third spot in the hexagonal on the final round .
This meant that after 10 failed qualification campaigns , Panama would appear at the World Cup for the first time in their history .
