At a score of 6 - 0 in favour of England at the 2018 World Cup , Felipe Baloy scored after a long free kick by Ricardo Avila for Panama 's first World Cup goal .
In the following match against Tunisia , Panama scored through an own goal by Tunisian defender Yassine Meriah . !
